{"tid":972198,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"在市場眼中， 學歷得呢三種class","createTime":"2019-01-07T08:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T09:54:22.000Z","uid":149978,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4ab33460224f1704f15f6173e5583366bdcb5c","tid":972198,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"1 General Education: 即係hkcee/hkale/hkdse/gce/ielts/toefl/sat/ib/gre/ap 等學歷及成績。<br />\n<br />\n2 專科教育：即係postsecondary cert/diploma, professional membership, diploma, high dip, associate degree, bachelor degree, postgraduate cert/diploma, master degree, license certificate 都係同屬此class . 非專科就同general education冇分別。所以好多大學讀純文科，讀左同冇讀差別不大。所以唔好以為hku/cuhk真係勁過ouhk/ive好多，在市場眼中，都係一樣專科資格。反而你讀的專業搵到食（例如醫護），你讀邊間大學都一撚樣。你讀乞食科，話知你hku/cuhk定係ouhk/ive，結果都係做唔返本行/搵唔到食。<br />\n<br />\n3 研究教育：即係MPhil/Ph.D。做研究相關行業好有用。如果唔做科研或學術研究，價值同general education或professional education差別不大。"},{"pid":"c147b44983cb3533892fdecf802b2cf8186e13ce","tid":972198,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfd213b6246e3ec0989db2385ef66932156fbf2","tid":972198,"uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c147b44983cb3533892fdecf802b2cf8186e13ce","tid":972198,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:28:52.000Z","msg":"讀書計，論重要性<br />\n<br />\n科 &gt; 程度（dip/high dip/aaso/degree/master）&gt; gpa &gt; 學校名氣"},{"pid":"4a97016e94d0df33969b08c254e7ba72bbec5989","tid":972198,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddfd213b6246e3ec0989db2385ef66932156fbf2","tid":972198,"uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c147b44983cb3533892fdecf802b2cf8186e13ce","tid":972198,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":